sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant UI as Public Holidays Management Page
    participant LW as Livewire Component
    participant DB as Database

    User->>UI: Open public holidays page
    UI->>LW: Initial request
    LW->>DB: Query current public holiday events
    DB-->>LW: Event list
    LW-->>UI: Render editable rows

    User->>UI: Edit holiday rows
    UI->>LW: Update bound row fields
    LW-->>UI: Keep draft state

    User->>UI: Save changes
    UI->>LW: save()
    LW->>DB: Upsert public holiday events + delete removed rows
    DB-->>LW: Persist completed
    LW-->>UI: Success toast

    User->>UI: Delete one event
    UI->>LW: deleteEvent(id)
    LW->>DB: Delete event row
    DB-->>LW: Deleted
    LW-->>UI: Refresh list
